(secondQuint)Needs Assessment Tool Integrated in Clinical Practice of Head and Neck Cancer Rehabilitation.

 The study tests a needs assessment and decision-making tool with patients surgically treated for Head and Neck Cancer.

 The tool will be an integrated part of a new clinical practice with nursing consultations at three seperate time-points in the post-surgical period of the patients.

 Half of the participants will receive nursing consultations using the tool and the other half will receive standard care.

